snippet.textDisplay: Now this is the kinda stuff that makes me want to be able to go to places like Japan, South Korea, Taiwan, and some other places in Asia at some point. I'm interested in trying a lot of stuff (or at least a lot of the less spicy stuff because I have a really sensitive tongue, heck I can't even stand things like pepperjack cheese), I want to see in person what everything looks like instead of just looking at a picture on a computer screen, and the culture - especially the mythology, folklore, fairytales, legends, music, and even the languages - is so fascinating to me. Heck I actually self-taught myself some Japanese, though I can't quite exactly identify the characters right off the bat lol
